entries.journal_entry_completion_summary: With a mixture of guile and firepower you were able to move around the Valarian Depot and get a complete inventory of everything that they got from the smuggled cargo. Commander Bastra was happy with the information and wants you to go and check out one more locale near the Darklighter Estate.
entries.journal_entry_description: The Valarian crime syndicate bought a portion of the cargo. According to your handler, the Rebel Carh'la Bastra,  that portion of the cargo was trans-shipped to a storage yard up in the mountains near Bestine. You need to infiltrate the facility and get a full inventory of what the Valarians bought.
entries.task00_comm_message_text: Who knew that the Jawas could have scavenged that much? Next I need you to go to a Valarian base. Uploading the information now.
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: The Valarian smuggling operation has set up a base in the mountains north of Bestine. Go there and reconn the area to see how you can infiltrate the base.
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: The Valarian portion of the cargo seems to be scattered throughout the site.You need to inventory all five pallets of cargo that make up the Valarian portion of the smuggled shipment.
